      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i was just sitting here in this cafe and realized i haven't spoken a single word to a human being in three days. like, if i just stopped showing up to work or stopped responding to texts... i don't think anyone would even notice for weeks. it feels like i'm just a ghost drifting through this city.",
