      "content": "i guess. but it’s more than just being quiet. it’s like... there’s no point in trying to be \"visible\" when there's nothing there to see. i feel like i've already vanished, and honestly, the idea of just actually being gone and not having to deal with the effort of existing anymore sounds way more peaceful than this.",
